SUMMARY:Frink Ridge Planting
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a restoration work party at Frink Park. \nWe will do some ground preparation and invasive plant removal and then plant native species in their place. \nRegister
URL:https://www.seattleparksfoundation.org/event/frink-ridge-planting/
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://www.seattleparksfoundation.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/home-NEW-2-Catherine-Anstett-Trolls-Knoll-gloves.jpg
