SUMMARY:Seattle Sensory Garden Volunteer Work Party
DESCRIPTION:Volunteer at Seattle Sensory Garden! \nJoin a work party and volunteer with others who care about this inclusive public space. \nLearn more about Seattle Sensory Garden here.
URL:https://www.seattleparksfoundation.org/event/seattle-sensory-garden-volunteer-work-party-8/
