SUMMARY:3rd Saturday forest restoration at Jackson Park Trail!
DESCRIPTION:Join a restoration work party at Jackson Park Golf Course. \nHelp restore native plants along this lovely trail around the public golf course. We’re out there every third Saturday. Enjoy the birds\, trees\, Thornton Creek\, and views into the golf course (and the occasional golf ball find!) \nLearn more + register
URL:https://www.seattleparksfoundation.org/event/3rd-saturday-forest-restoration-at-jackson-park-trail-22/
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://www.seattleparksfoundation.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/home-NEW-2-Catherine-Anstett-Trolls-Knoll-gloves.jpg
