SUMMARY:solstice tree planting at Mount Baker Park
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a restoration work party at Mount Baker Park. \nHappy solstice everyone! It’s winter\, it’s wet\, there’s mud\, we love it. come celebrate native plant stewards favorite holiday. \nLearn more + register
URL:https://www.seattleparksfoundation.org/event/solstice-tree-plant/
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://www.seattleparksfoundation.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/home-NEW-2-Catherine-Anstett-Trolls-Knoll-gloves.jpg
