UID:205145-1766322000-1766329200@www.seattleparksfoundation.org
SUMMARY:Cheasty Forest at Hanford Steps
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a restoration work party at Cheasty GS: Cheasty Blvd. \nWe will plant shrubs\, ferns and wild flowers. Then mulch with a thick layer of woodchips\, that will keep the the soil moist and suppress weeds. \nRegister \nLearn more about Cheasty Greenspace here.
URL:https://www.seattleparksfoundation.org/event/cheasty-forest-at-hanford-steps-22/
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://www.seattleparksfoundation.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Cheasty-Trails-lead.jpg
END:VEVENT
