SUMMARY:Scotch Broom Patrol
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a restoration work party at Discovery Park. \nScotch broom really stands out this time of year (especially in the brown meadows) and are easy to pull in the wet soils. We’ve got extractigators\, weed wrenches\, uprooters and heavy-duty shovels to remove these prolific pests. \nRegister
URL:https://www.seattleparksfoundation.org/event/scotch-broom-patrol-4/
