SUMMARY:Forest Restoration - Longfellow Creek at Graham Street
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a restoration work party at Longfellow Creek GS: Delridge Natural Area. \nYou and your fellow volunteers will participate in hands-on conservation work. This event will be some combination of removing invasive plant\, planting native plants\, and putting down wood chips\, based on how far we get in the previous event. \nRegister
